OL,6,FWith Russia's invasion of Ukraine now
OL,7,Fin its third year, how the UK invests
OL,8,Fin its military to meet new threats is
OL,9,Fvery much at the top of the political
OL,10,Fagenda, with the UK Government
OL,11,Fannouncing an extra #75billion to
OL,12,Frespond to the threat of authoritarian
OL,13,Fstates.
OL,15,FRoyal Welsh soldiers are among those
OL,16,Ftraining in Poland on the exercise
OL,17,Fdesigned to boost the ability of
OL,18,Fallies like the UK and US to work
OL,19,Ftogether, should they need to, with
OL,20,Farmed forces adapting combat
OL,21,Ftechniques to face new global threats.
