OL,3,COn patrol with Royal Welsh soldiers on
OL,4,CNATO's biggest exercise in a generation
OL,6,FCorporal Danny Nye, from the 1st
OL,7,FBattalion The , said: "When I joined
OL,8,Fit was , now it's very focused on what
OL,9,FRussia is doing.
OL,11,F"We've had to re-learn things for a
OL,12,Fdifferent theatre, lots of things that
OL,13,Fwould work in don't work here."
OL,15,FLieutenant Colonel Ed Wilcox, of the
OL,16,Fsame battalion, echoed this, saying:
OL,17,F"Of course the situation in Ukraine is
OL,18,Fa backdrop to this exercise, and we
OL,19,Fabsolutely stand in solidarity with
OL,20,Fthe brave Ukrainians in that fight.
