OL,6,F"This location is not coincidental but
OL,7,FI think by being here we make Russia's
OL,8,Factions in Ukraine less likely
OL,9,Felsewhere in Europe."
OL,11,FEight hundred vehicles have been
OL,12,Ftransported to Poland for the training
OL,13,Fexercise involving 90,000 troops
OL,14,Foverall, with 16,000 British troops
OL,15,Fmoving through Europe for the task.
OL,17,FIt's the first time Welsh reservists
OL,18,Fhave taken part.
