OL,7,F3rd Battalion The Royal Welsh, is an
OL,8,FAnglesey park ranger in his day job.
OL,10,F"We've got a great team working on
OL,11,FAnglesey doing that role and also
OL,12,Fworking through the Royal Welsh," he
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"It's a very similar but also quite
OL,16,Fdifferent role. This is slightly more
OL,17,Fadrenaline-filled and action-packed."
