OL,7,Fground in Poland and pledged a boost
OL,8,Fto defence spending, promising a total
OL,9,Fannual spend of #87billion by 2030.
OL,10,FThe defence secretary called it
OL,11,F"precisely what the armed forces
OL,12,Fneeded".
OL,14,FBut shadow defence secretary John
OL,15,FHealey wasn't so sure, saying: "You
OL,16,Fcant deter Putin with press releases."
